schools.name: Ann Brock El At Oak Grove

data.description: Charming 3 bedroom 2 bath, over 1700 square foot home! Very highly maintained in the subdivision of Ashford Park. This property has an open study ideal for running a business, working from home or can be considered a play area. Included is a nice size laundry room along with an open concept style kitchen and living room. This home has updated brick, windows, air condition unit and water heater! Spend this summer at the community pool! Minutes from I35 to commute anywhere in the Metroplex.
